<div id="review_4240997276" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4240997276" />
    <a title="Stephen R." class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/89281938-stephen-r"><img alt="Stephen R." src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1549132945p2/89281938.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4240997276?book_show_action=true">Sep 16, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Stephen R." class="user" itemprop="url" name="Stephen R." href="/user/show/89281938-stephen-r">Stephen R.</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4240997276" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2483494452083919281">This collection of essays from some of the most well-respected scholars and researchers in the world offers a comprehensive guide to improving the future for humans. It takes an in-depth look at the technology which could be utilized to achieve a healthier, happier, and longer existence for the human race, with long-term solutions to some of the biggest issues we currently face on earth. <br/><br/>The essays are written in a style that makes them accessible to the masses, and maintains the reader&apos;s intere</span>
  <span id="freeText2483494452083919281" style="display:none">This collection of essays from some of the most well-respected scholars and researchers in the world offers a comprehensive guide to improving the future for humans. It takes an in-depth look at the technology which could be utilized to achieve a healthier, happier, and longer existence for the human race, with long-term solutions to some of the biggest issues we currently face on earth. <br /><br />The essays are written in a style that makes them accessible to the masses, and maintains the reader's interest. It is a mammoth book that would be best enjoyed in several short sittings and revisited time and time again.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="2483494452083919281" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
