  <div class="friendReviews elementListBrown" >
    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3243061996" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3243061996" />
    <a title="Marcela Melnic" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/60184540-marcela-melnic"><img alt="Marcela Melnic" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1527631763p2/60184540.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3243061996?book_show_action=true">Mar 23, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marcela Melnic" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marcela Melnic" href="/user/show/60184540-marcela-melnic">Marcela Melnic</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3243061996" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9818930419805643695">We should all know how important preventive medicine is, especially in light of the current coronavirus pandemics due to novel COVID-19. The Transhumanism Handbook has devoted 15 chapters out of 66 on physical and mental health. A big emphasis is placed on rejuvenation of our mind and body through science and technology, so that we will become immune to all diseases. The book offers achievable long-term solutions, not short-term fixes, to ensure the survival of the human race. I love the ideas, </span>
  <span id="freeText9818930419805643695" style="display:none">We should all know how important preventive medicine is, especially in light of the current coronavirus pandemics due to novel COVID-19. The Transhumanism Handbook has devoted 15 chapters out of 66 on physical and mental health. A big emphasis is placed on rejuvenation of our mind and body through science and technology, so that we will become immune to all diseases. The book offers achievable long-term solutions, not short-term fixes, to ensure the survival of the human race. I love the ideas, and I am following a plenty of good advice from the handbook!<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="9818930419805643695" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


