    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3769468272" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3769468272" />
    <a title="Elisanda Koziner" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/128412016-elisanda-koziner"><img alt="Elisanda Koziner" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3769468272?book_show_action=true">Jan 13, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Elisanda Koziner" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Elisanda Koziner" href="/user/show/128412016-elisanda-koziner">Elisanda Koziner</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3769468272" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17154429013837072808">“The Transhumanism Handbook” offers a vision for us humans to transcend current threats and uprising global crisis. Transhumanism develops new survival technologies and promotes policies to save our earth and its inhabitants from being destroyed by human activities and natural disasters. Today more than ever and considering the current global COVID 19 pandemic “humanity has to come together…to turn ideas into useful technology” and commit to &quot;settle conflict, overcome hatred and defend shared va</span>
  <span id="freeText17154429013837072808" style="display:none">“The Transhumanism Handbook” offers a vision for us humans to transcend current threats and uprising global crisis. Transhumanism develops new survival technologies and promotes policies to save our earth and its inhabitants from being destroyed by human activities and natural disasters. Today more than ever and considering the current global COVID 19 pandemic “humanity has to come together…to turn ideas into useful technology” and commit to "settle conflict, overcome hatred and defend shared values" – “ONLY TOGETHER”<br /><br />I started reading “The Transhumanism Handbook” in lockdown, feeling powerless, stuck and frustrated about the global situation, including all the bad news we humans, are exposed to in daily media. Transhumanism has a desire to build a world worth living in. This requires critical thinking and the willingness to discover the unknown, alternative ideas and practices for humanity to transcend present beliefs. Reading this, gave me hope. It inspired me to continue facing these hard times of uncertainty. <br /><br />Transhumanism provides a forecast of humanity’s future by re-evaluating and reassessing humanity from past to present. It deals with reality, knowledge &amp; existence, and offers a cultural understanding of human integration with technology. It provides techniques for observing how technology is shaping society and investigates the ethical outcomes, questioning traditional norms of society.<br /><br />Its believed that human lifespan can be extended, aging can be reversed, death is optional. Artificial intelligence is used to improve the human condition. Nanotechnology can resolve environmental hazards; genetic engineering can mitigate diseases. The book explains that there are limitations to these statements, such as religion, beliefs, rules, law and continues to explain that humans are explorers by nature, who enjoy challenges to ameliorate problems and uncover the unknown to transcend these precise limitations. In order for us humans to transcend, the book suggests to "Go outside to gain perspective to achieve evolutionary transformation."<br />Humans have no final stage of evolution. <br /><br />"Transhumanism prepares us to be leaders of our own lives and work with others to increase the well-being of others" - Especially considering the current COVID 19 crisis, Transhumanism is showing us that the world as humanity, we humans, need to transcend, we need to gather and share our knowledge in all fields to come-up with treatment and a cure for this global health threat.<br /> <br />According to Kurzweil within a quarter century, non-biological intelligence will match the range of human intelligence and soar past it, because of the acceleration of information-based technologies and the abilities of machines to instantly share knowledge. Eventually nano robots will be integrated in our bodies overcoming illness, providing longevity &amp; intelligence. New technologies will always outgrow those technologies imposing barriers to development.<br /> <br />"Biological evolution allowed the appearance of human beings &amp; other species, through millions of years of natural selection based on trials and errors." Today we can control biological evolution, direct it, interfere, and go beyond it. Moravec argues that robots will be our rightful descendants and he explains several ways to upload a mind into a robot. Warwick in the UK is a cybernetics pioneer, who implants microchips into his own body. He wants to become a cyborg.<br /><br /> <br />"The more we engage in the unknown, the more we adapt to change, the more we challenge our own thinking, the more impactful our shared knowledge will address challenges faced." This part is also very important to current COVID times, which are so uncertain, and we are almost forced by law to adapt to what we are told, not knowing a truth. We are just listening to media and following the rules. But we believe in the threat and we have seen that the pandemic is real. As humans and as a global society, we are adapting to challenges and threats to our health but are also living with many restrictions and in complete uncertainty. COVID 19 has changed our daily lives and we have moved along and accepted the changes.<br /> <br />"Thanks to technological evolution, humans will transcend our biological limitations to become transhuman and eventually posthumans. To ease the transition, we need to prepare for possibilities. Future life form will continue evolving.”<br /> <br /><br /><br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="17154429013837072808" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


